title: 2 Bed/1 Bath Apartment in Minneapolis
posting_body: ['Available now.', 'Another new listing brought to you by The Feland Team and Renters Warehouse.', 'This vintage 1920’s apartment has hardwood flooring, great architectural and woodwork details as well as new landscaping and a perennial garden to enjoy.', 'Walk into the spacious living room with lots of natural light and then to the dining area, with gorgeous built-ins, adjacent to the kitchen The kitchen has stainless appliances, granite counters, a gas stove and lots of cabinet space.', 'Both bedrooms and the bathroom are nicely updated as well.', 'Single car, detached garage stall included, laundry available in building.', 'Pets considered with an additional $300 deposit.', 'Tenant pays electric, gas, cable and phone.', 'Please note there is a $55 application fee.', 'Also, all properties have a one-time $199 lease admin fee and a monthly processing fee of 1% of the rent.', 'This home is not currently qualified for housing assistance programs such as section 8.', 'To book a showing on this property, go to <URL> and scroll down to the property of interest.']
